game.name: Hello Kitty Beach Fun
game.description:
Summer season has just come and all people are planning to go to cool locations! The cute hello kitty is also no different from others and has decided to go on a beach holiday today. But, she is confused what to put on. Would you dare to guide her to make her holiday unforgettable? Join Hello Kitty Beach Fun game and get ready to help her to prepare for the wonderful holiday! Hurry up, friends! You would have plenty of things to do to give her a comfortable holiday. 
Hello Kitty has been boring for long. It is up to you how to make her weekend holiday so special on the beach in this brand new dressing game for girls. Your first job is to help her find and pack all the things she asks for during the weekend. Also give her a nice clothing item and make all the other arrangements to allow her make a comfortable holiday. Do not forget to decorate the place with the items available on the screen. 
Collect all the items, including goggle, ball, and hat and then help her choose a nice outfit! Choose from different types of tops, a nice pair of shoes, matching hats, and lovely goggles in this free online html5 princess dress up game! Make sure to arrange a lovely chair on the beach and an umbrella. Complete all the three steps to allow Hello Kitty a fabulous weekend holiday! Check out more princess dress up games on atmegame.com where you can play games online, no download required!
